node.text:
My upcoming variant incentive cover to🔺Bermuda🔻 #2 has been revealed! This is a fun new creator owned book drawn by @nkwbradshaw and written by John Layman and is in stores Aug 18 through @idwpublishing 

Colors by @sabine_rich . I had fun working in the triangle and crop-circle design motifs into my layout and echoing the pose to fit that same triangular shape. It’s fun to occasionally still do more unusual new ideas and characters. 

#bermuda #bermudatriangle #jscottcampbell #drawing #comicbooks #art #comicbookart #idw #idwcomics #adventure

node.text: I’ve been seeing online that it’s the 40th anniversary of one of my top 3 favorite films of all time Raiders of the Lost Ark! Several years ago I drew some 1 of 1 sketch cards that were hidden in random packs of Topps Indiana Jones trading cards! ⏪Swipe⏪ through to see my “Raiders” cards retelling the story of Raiders with accompaniment from John Williams, assuming the IG algorithm doesn’t strip the music out! #indianajones #indianajonesandtheraidersofthelostark #raidersofthelostark #raidersofthelostark40 #harrisonford #indianajones5 #jscottcampbell #topps #georgelucas #stevenspielberg #johnwilliams
